title: Regő Szánthó
text:
Regő Szánthó (born 22 November 2000) is a <a href="Hungary">Hungarian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Midfielder%20%28association%20football%29">midfielder</a> who plays for <a href="Zalaegerszegi%20TE">Zalaegerszegi TE</a> on loan from <a href="Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20I">OTP Bank Liga</a> club <a href="Ferencv%C3%A1rosi%20TC%20%28football%29">Ferencvárosi TC</a>.
Club career.
Ferencváros.
On 16 June 2020, he became champion with Ferencváros by beating <a href="Budapest%20Honv%C3%A9d%20FC">Budapest Honvéd FC</a> at the <a href="Hidegkuti%20N%C3%A1ndor%20Stadion">Hidegkuti Nándor Stadion</a> on the 30th match day of the <a href="2019%E2%80%9320%20Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20I">2019–20 Nemzeti Bajnokság I</a> season.
